    "description": "<div>This layer contains census tract centroids with attributes about household income in the past 12 months (in 2016 inflation-adjusted dollars). These are from the American Community Survey (ACS) 2016 5-year estimates. Table B19001. <br /></div><div><br /></div><div>Map is rendered to show the quantity of households within each area. <br /></div><div><br /></div><div>Data downloaded from the US Census <a href='https://factfinder.census.gov/faces/nav/jsf/pages/download_center.xhtml#' target='_blank'>American Fact Finder</a>.<br /></div><div><br /></div><div>The data is provided in the following income ranges. The national figure and margin of error are also provided (also from ACS):</div><div><table border='0' cellpadding='0' cellspacing='0' style='border-collapse:\n collapse;width:303pt' width='403'>\n \n \n \n <tbody><tr height='21' style='height:15.75pt'>\n  <td height='21' style='height:15.75pt;width:143pt' width='190'>Income\n  Ranges</td>\n  <td style='width:80pt' width='106'>National Figure</td>\n  <td style='width:80pt' width='107'>Margin of Error</td>\n </tr>\n <tr height='20' style='height:15.0pt'>\n  <td height='20' style='height:15.0pt'>Total (USA)</td>\n  <td>117,716,237</td>\n  <td>+/-222,078</td>\n </tr>\n <tr height='20' style='height:15.0pt'>\n  <td height='20' style='height:15.0pt;width:143pt' width='190'>Less\n  than $10,000</td>\n  <td>8,243,664</td>\n  <td>+/-18,695</td>\n </tr>\n <tr height='20' style='height:15.0pt'>\n  <td height='20' style='height:15.0pt;width:143pt' width='190'>$10,000\n  to $14,999</td>\n  <td>6,000,362</td>\n  <td>+/-20,040</td>\n </tr>\n <tr height='20' style='height:15.0pt'>\n  <td height='20' style='height:15.0pt;width:143pt' width='190'>$15,000\n  to $19,999</td>\n  <td>5,958,713</td>\n  <td>+/-16,104</td>\n </tr>\n <tr height='20' style='height:15.0pt'>\n  <td height='20' style='height:15.0pt;width:143pt' width='190'>$20,000\n  to $24,999</td>\n  <td>6,094,929</td>\n  <td>+/-15,803</td>\n </tr>\n <tr height='20' style='height:15.0pt'>\n  <td height='20' style='height:15.0pt;width:143pt' width='190'>$25,000\n  to $29,999</td>\n  <td>5,771,744</td>\n  <td>+/-15,216</td>\n </tr>\n <tr height='20' style='height:15.0pt'>\n  <td height='20' style='height:15.0pt;width:143pt' width='190'>$30,000\n  to $34,999</td>\n  <td>5,856,803</td>\n  <td>+/-14,451</td>\n </tr>\n <tr height='20' style='height:15.0pt'>\n  <td height='20' style='height:15.0pt;width:143pt' width='190'>$35,000\n  to $39,999</td>\n  <td>5,404,041</td>\n  <td>+/-15,856</td>\n </tr>\n <tr height='20' style='height:15.0pt'>\n  <td height='20' style='height:15.0pt;width:143pt' width='190'>$40,000\n  to $44,999</td>\n  <td>5,408,687</td>\n  <td>+/-15,420</td>\n </tr>\n <tr height='20' style='height:15.0pt'>\n  <td height='20' style='height:15.0pt;width:143pt' width='190'>$45,000\n  to $49,999</td>\n  <td>4,775,997</td>\n  <td>+/-15,271</td>\n </tr>\n <tr height='20' style='height:15.0pt'>\n  <td height='20' style='height:15.0pt;width:143pt' width='190'>$50,000\n  to $59,999</td>\n  <td>9,199,672</td>\n  <td>+/-22,260</td>\n </tr>\n <tr height='20' style='height:15.0pt'>\n  <td height='20' style='height:15.0pt;width:143pt' width='190'>$60,000\n  to $74,999</td>\n  <td>11,714,107</td>\n  <td>+/-31,281</td>\n </tr>\n <tr height='20' style='height:15.0pt'>\n  <td height='20' style='height:15.0pt;width:143pt' width='190'>$75,000\n  to $99,999</td>\n  <td>14,361,853</td>\n  <td>+/-53,518</td>\n </tr>\n <tr height='20' style='height:15.0pt'>\n  <td height='20' style='height:15.0pt;width:143pt' width='190'>$100,000\n  to $124,999</td>\n  <td>9,856,915</td>\n  <td>+/-44,470</td>\n </tr>\n <tr height='20' style='height:15.0pt'>\n  <td height='20' style='height:15.0pt;width:143pt' width='190'>$125,000\n  to $149,999</td>\n  <td>6,028,908</td>\n  <td>+/-33,311</td>\n </tr>\n <tr height='20' style='height:15.0pt'>\n  <td height='20' style='height:15.0pt;width:143pt' width='190'>$150,000\n  to $199,999</td>\n  <td>6,369,156</td>\n  <td>+/-36,256</td>\n </tr>\n <tr height='21' style='height:15.75pt'>\n  <td height='21' style='height:15.75pt;width:143pt' width='190'>$200,000\n  or more</td>\n  <td>6,670,686</td>\n  <td>+/-37,386</td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
